    "Our study adheres to the Preferred Reporting Items for Systematic Reviews and Meta-Analyses (PRISMA) guidelines (Moher et al. 2009).",
    "In alignment with these guidelines, we initiated our literature search by developing targeted search queries for academic databases.",
